  "body": "<p>As much as I love to travel to teach classes all over the world, the reality is that I just cannot get to most places. Someone needs to invent teleportation! Until then, I am excited to announce that Jamie Waters and I are launching our first class together, The Creative Life: Documented!  It's a five part online workshop featuring over <strong>50</strong> never before seen projects that just went live!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b99886042af87b04.jpg?v=1782538976\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Earlier this year we launched \"The Creative Handbook,\" a free e-book and video course which has been downloaded by over 7,000 participants! This overwhelmingly positive feedback we received inspired us to get to work on an even bigger project together, one that required a lot of crafting and creativity. We've spent a lot of time and energy, and have worked really hard to create the projects in this class and would love for you to be a part of it!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d12f51a8acdcd013.jpg?v=1782538979\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>With five kids and two business between us, we know what it means to be busy, so with The Creative Life: Documented, we are revealing our best tips and techniques to help you get creative and squeeze more out of your time, so you can get more of life’s moments documented.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fb4c3016ef8eb0f7.jpg?v=1782538981\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And as a special incentive, all students who register by 11:59pm PST on Saturday, November 7th will get a free mini book shipped right to their door! Yay for happy mail! We've made a video to tell you all about the class, click here to learn more. Thanks in advance for sharing our excitement and we hope to see you in the classroom!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}